{"type": "article", "id": 15939, "title": "The Darwin Tank", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-12T07:11:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135548XA7OjeFh2zMiUTIE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在家中拥有一个小的水族馆不是不可能，来自比利时的团队专门研究了适合水母生活的水缸，他们使用了一个泵来过滤水而不会伤害到水母，并配有 LED 灯。外面罩着的玻璃将水母放大了一倍，当灯光透过水缸照射在墙上时，映射出半透明的水母在轻盈舒展的唯美画面。直接透过水缸看事物时，也都像染上了梦幻色彩。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/815660157/the-darwin-tank-an-original-jellyfish-tank\" target=\"_blank\">该产品正在Kickstarter 上集资以获得进一步改善</a>。<a href=\"http://www.darwinsect.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看团队的其他作品。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143404Kls2D3iyRwZ4NW01.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143405jP5hLRyCDkOUz0T4.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614340567t0uDJT3jOsladf.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143405mIBKFk7SthaMygD6.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"382\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}